"The :guilabel:`Repository server` can be specified in the UMC module "
":guilabel:`Repository Settings`."
msgstr ""
"Im UMC-Modul :guilabel:`Repository-Einstellungen` kann der :guilabel"
":`Repository-Server` festgelegt werden."

#: ../../software/repository-server.rst:54
msgid "Configuration via Univention Configuration Registry"
msgstr "Konfiguration über Univention Configuration Registry"

#: ../../software/repository-server.rst:56
msgid ""
"The repository server to be used can be entered in the |UCSUCRV| "
":envvar:`repository/online/server` and is preset to ``updates.software-"
"univention.de`` for a new installation."
msgstr ""
"Der zu verwendende Repository-Server wird in die |UCSUCRV| "
